    <h1>About MatchBox</h1>
    <p>MatchBox is a native Rust implementation of BoxLang. It provides:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Zero-JVM overhead</li>
        <li>Sub-millisecond startup times</li>
        <li>Built-in High Performance Web Server</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="footer">Server Port: <bx:output>#cgi.server_port#</bx:output></div>
